<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
    <h2 style="color: #dc3545;">⚠️ Allerta Scorta Minima</h2>
    <p>Il seguente prodotto ha raggiunto o superato la soglia minima di magazzino:</p>

    <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 20px 0;">
      <tr>
        <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd; font-weight: bold;">Prodotto</td>
        <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;"><%= @product.nome_oggetto %></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd; font-weight: bold;">Quantità attuale</td>
        <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd; color: #dc3545;">
          <strong><%= @product.quantita_disponibile %></strong>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd; font-weight: bold;">Soglia minima</td>
        <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;"><%= @product.soglia_minima_magazzino %></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd; font-weight: bold;">Tipo</td>
        <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;"><%= @product.product_type&.nome_tipo %></td>
      </tr>
    </table>

    <p>Accedi al pannello per effettuare un nuovo ordine:</p>
    <div style="text-align: center; margin: 20px 0;">
      <a href="http://localhost:3001"
         style="background-color: #dc3545; color: white; padding: 12px 30px;
                text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold;">
        Vai al Pannello
      </a>
    </div>

    <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #eee; margin: 20px 0;">
    <p style="color: #999; font-size: 12px;">ERAMUS SRL — Sistema Gestionale</p>
  </body>
</html>